Zype-CLI

== How to install

1. Build gem

gem build zype-cli.gemspec 

2. Install gem

gem install ./zype-cli-0.0.0.gem

== How to use

1. Open irb

irb

2. Require gem

require 'zype-cli'

3. Configure gem

# For a rails application add the following under:
# config/initializers/zype-cli.rb

ZypeCli.configure do |config| 
  config.api_key = [your api key]
  config.host    = [host] # default: api.zype-core.com
  config.port    = [port] # default: 3000
  config.use_ssl = false  # default: false
end

4. Create a client

ZypeCli::Client.new

3. Query zobjects

client.zobjects.all(zobject: 'team')
